{"tid":2127410,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"如果KPOP界翻拍幻愛 係咪德國腸同娜璉做男女主角？","createTime":"2020-07-27T10:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T06:25:25.000Z","uid":152123,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e148396e25f89abfd92f6187490e26217bb97999","tid":2127410,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:01:18.000Z","msg":"善良戇直的德國粉絲阿Josh，是精神分裂症未康復者，雖然渴望愛情但從來不敢戀愛。偶然機遇下，他在Youtube偶遇了清麗脫俗的韓國偶像娜璉，一見鍾情卻掙扎應否透露病情。<br />\n<br />\n躊躇之際，不幸再次病發，被幻覺纏繞。他更發現她的真正身分，竟然是個攻於心計的閪女人？二人發展出一段懸疑曲折的禁戀，疑幻似真。"},{"pid":"5f72f1e4631dba49d3b71d208208c8f18c056618","tid":2127410,"uid":143093,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:03:00.000Z","msg":"但幻愛女主唔係公廁"},{"pid":"0f3eeffe5814c51e53182877bcf75caf03594bcf","tid":2127410,"uid":25924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed21cce02978928852938f60a1a90de20f6177fb","tid":2127410,"uid":193951,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5f72f1e4631dba49d3b71d208208c8f18c056618","tid":2127410,"uid":143093,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:03:00.000Z","msg":"但幻愛女主唔係公廁"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:04:17.000Z","msg":"你有冇睇㗎"},{"pid":"a50fcb6b359bfa949653dd5eb633042df5196a95","tid":2127410,"uid":152123,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"5f72f1e4631dba49d3b71d208208c8f18c056618","tid":2127410,"uid":143093,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:03:00.000Z","msg":"但幻愛女主唔係公廁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/104408_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F104408_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f6